---
---
<div id="about" class="min-h-screen relative px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 py-24 flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="flex gap-4 items-center justify-start mb-12 animate-[fade-in-right_1s_ease-out]">
      <div class="h-10 w-2 bg-accent-red rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(225,29,72,0.8)]"></div>
      <h2 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-outfit font-bold tracking-tight">About Me</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start relative z-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_0.3s_both]">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <p class="text-justify text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
            With a proven track record across Indonesia, Singapore, and the United States, I bring a wealth of international experience delivering impactful software solutions. Trusted to lead and complete diverse projects spanning social media platforms, ERP systems, supply chain management, banking software, content management systems, and job portals, I thrive in dynamic environments that demand adaptability and technical excellence.
          </p>
          <p class="text-justify text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            My technical toolkit is broad and deep, encompassing multiple programming languages such as <span class="text-white font-medium">Golang, JavaScript, Python, Ruby, and PHP</span>. I am proficient in a variety of modern frameworks including Rails, Go Fiber, Go Gin, Go Echo, Laravel, Django, Next.js, and Angular, enabling me to craft scalable, maintainable, and high-performance applications tailored to business needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_0.5s_both]">
        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-l-accent-red group hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent-red" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
            Full-Stack Development Mastery
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">Skilled in a broad spectrum of programming languages and frameworks, enabling me to build scalable and maintainable applications tailored to diverse business needs.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-l-accent-red group hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent-red" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
            DevOps & Agile Expertise
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">Proficient in Git, Docker, and CI/CD pipelines, combined with hands-on experience in Agile Scrum methodologies to streamline development and deployment processes.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-l-accent-red group hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent-red" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            Global Project Experience
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">Proven ability to adapt and deliver in multicultural environments, managing complex projects in various industries with a focus on quality and innovation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section id="experiences" class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 bg-dark-bg relative border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_right,_var(--color-dark-card)_0%,_transparent_70%)] opacity-30 z-0 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="mb-16 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_both] text-center md:text-left">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
        <div class="h-[2px] w-12 bg-accent-red shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(225,29,72,0.8)]"></div>
        <span class="text-accent-red font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">Work History</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-outfit font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Dive Into My<br/><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-slate-500">Career Story</span></h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto md:mx-0 text-lg">From pivotal moments that sparked my passion to challenges that fueled my growth, a walkthrough of the experiences, achievements, and turning points that define my professional path.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Grid Layout -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 relative">
      
      <!-- Entry 1 -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-dark-card/80 transition-colors border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
          <span class="text-6xl font-black text-accent-red leading-none">01</span>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-accent-red bg-accent-red/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 border border-accent-red/20 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(225,29,72,0.2)]">Apr 2023 — Present</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">PT. Solusi Pembayaran Elektronik</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Software Engineer</span> • Indonesia
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
          {['PHP', 'Golang', 'Laravel', 'Yii', 'Fiber', 'GRPC'].map(tag => (
            <span class="text-xs font-medium border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-slate-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg group-hover:border-accent-red/50 transition-colors">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 2 -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-dark-card/80 transition-colors border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
          <span class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-400 leading-none">02</span>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 border border-white/10">Oct 2022 — Nov 2022</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Forest Technologies</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Tech Lead</span> • Singapore
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
          {['Golang', 'Angular', 'GRPC', 'MongoDB', 'Docker', 'GCP'].map(tag => (
            <span class="text-xs font-medium border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-slate-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg group-hover:border-accent-red/50 transition-colors">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 3 -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-dark-card/80 transition-colors border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
          <span class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-400 leading-none">03</span>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 border border-white/10">Jan 2022 — Sep 2022</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Forest Technologies</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Software Engineer</span> • Singapore
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
          {['Golang', 'Angular', 'Javascript', 'GRPC', 'MongoDB'].map(tag => (
            <span class="text-xs font-medium border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-slate-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg group-hover:border-accent-red/50 transition-colors">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 4 -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-dark-card/80 transition-colors border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
          <span class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-400 leading-none">04</span>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 border border-white/10">Feb 2020 — Feb 2021</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Cendekia Muda Digimedia</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Backend Developer</span> • Indonesia
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
          {['Golang', 'Echo', 'GORM', 'HTML', 'CSS'].map(tag => (
            <span class="text-xs font-medium border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-slate-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg group-hover:border-accent-red/50 transition-colors">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
